data.description: Don't miss this stunning custom home by Woods Brothers.  Gorgeous sprawling ranch with a Rocky Mountain View and so many special touches.  Open plan with a beautiful kitchen.  Huge pantry and island, pot filler, copper farm sink, and stainless appliances.  The refrigerator features a built-in Keurig for your morning coffee.  The owner's suite is luxurious, with a huge shower,  copper soaking tub, and custom towel warmers.  Don't miss the Jack and Jill bathroom with exposed brick.  Tall wood stained doors and a cozy fireplace add to the ambience.  The second level features a bonus room with a separate split air unit--perfect for tv, gaming, an office, or extra sleeping space.  This lovely home has a huge 3-car garage and sits on 9.5 acres that is fenced and ready for your horses!   Fabulous location, near Cheyenne and Laramie.  Live your best life in this country dream!
